    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>139</ID>
      <DefaultText>"Then it was the Godhammer symbol I saw extinguished on your staff."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>140</ID>
      <DefaultText>Trigger Conv Node 140</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>143</ID>
      <DefaultText>"You still see them." His tone is more level, more curious, but there is a challenge in it. "Not all can." He raises an eyebrow. "But then again, few have a Watcher's... gift... of sight."</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
